reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful but inconsistent when buying a set, colors are off
reviews.reviewText: I am unsure of how to reach the seller, I have looked and do not see a way to reach the seller to discuss when buying a pair the second cabinets do not match as I have seen in another review. I purchased a pair of them to make one entertainment center console for my TV. It is unfortunate that it is the main focal point of the room. The cabinets are two different shades when you buy them in a pair. Other than that, I think these are such beautiful cabinets. It’s a shame that my eyes are drawn to the different colors. You can see that one of the cabinets come with just tan woven rattan doors & the second set comes with green and brown and light rattan weaved into it instead of just tan to match the other. I don’t mind either color I just would like it to be consistent. In the pictures, the cabinet on the left has greens and browns and different colors weaved into the door and the cabinet on the right just has tan rattan weaved together. I have included many pictures of them, and I have included separate pictures of them. This is just for others to be aware that when you buy them as a pair, they may not come the same color. But wow, they really are beautiful, easy to put together, the perfect height and I love them! Also, they came so carefully packaged and padded that, despite the driver putting holes in the box, they were still in perfect condition. And not at all cheap and awful looking when you take them out of the box as I saw another review. This is one of the best fake wood cabinets I’ve ever seen when it comes to sturdiness and the condition of the wood.!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is CUTE and affordable
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I am SUPER impressed with this little sideboard for the price. It is not real wood but does not look cheap, so if you’re looking for the natural look, this is it. It’s a light wood and color is true to the pictures.It was very simple to put together and feels sturdy. I keep mentioning price but for the cost, I’m very impressed.The inside has three adjustable shelves that can be moved around, we used it as a game cabinet which was super functional for us. As you can see in the photo we were able to fill it so it has a lot of space for it’s size.I’d buy again! Don’t sleep on this one.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: For the price I think this was a good purchase. It’s particle board, but looks nice and was pretty easy to put together. Feels pretty sturdy and has a lot of room inside. Overall I’m very happy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Amazon lacked here.
reviews.reviewText: Purchased this in a set. The first one was beautiful and went together great and easy. The second one ended up being damaged. The rattan was defective and was torn up. We didn’t realize until we put it together. Amazon refused to take it back unless we packaged the whole thing back up perfectly in the box.I asked to be refunded as I didn’t want to take apart the entire thing. They refused. So now I have to keep a defective cabinet.
